memberdef.name: MYGUI_EXCEPT
memberdef.initializer: { \ MYGUI_LOG(Critical, dest); \ MYGUI_DBG_BREAK;\ std::ostringstream stream; \ stream << dest << "\n"; \ MYGUI_BASE_EXCEPT(stream.str().c_str(), "MyGUI"); \ }

memberdef.name: MYGUI_ASSERT
memberdef.initializer: { \ if ( ! (exp) ) \ { \ MYGUI_LOG(Critical, dest); \ MYGUI_DBG_BREAK;\ std::ostringstream stream; \ stream << dest << "\n"; \ MYGUI_BASE_EXCEPT(stream.str().c_str(), "MyGUI"); \ } \ }

memberdef.name: MYGUI_ASSERT_RANGE
memberdef.initializer: MYGUI_ASSERT(index < size, owner << " : index number " << index << " out of range [" << size << "]");

memberdef.name: MYGUI_ASSERT_RANGE_AND_NONE
memberdef.initializer: MYGUI_ASSERT(index < size || index == ITEM_NONE, owner << " : index number " << index << " out of range [" << size << "]");

memberdef.name: MYGUI_ASSERT_RANGE_INSERT
memberdef.initializer: MYGUI_ASSERT((index <= size) || (index == MyGUI::ITEM_NONE), owner << " : insert index number " << index << " out of range [" << size << "] or not ITEM_NONE");
